description:
Shinonome Nagi, a college student who loves reading sensual novels in the newsports column, met with a writer he admires, the sensual novelist Shidou Tatsuo.

Shidou treats him like a child and swears that he could make him come with just a kiss &ndash; as it turns out, Shido's kiss technique was truly outstanding!

Since their first meeting, Nagi and Shidou got involved in intercrural sex, an encounter that inspired Shidou to produce a story which got him a new serialization!

&quot;Be my assistant and cooperate with me to produce the story, perverted brat.&quot;

&quot;Stop calling me a brat, old man!&quot;
